      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "# \uD83C\uDFC6 MIDGAME SURVIVAL GUIDE\n\n### \uD83C\uDF10 Zone Positioning\n-  ⭕  **Target Dead Sides**\n  - Rotate toward the circle edge furthest from the bus path . which is also known as Dead-Side\n  * This keeps you away from stacked teams Rotating out their Stacked POI's \n  * Try and Rotate Deadside everytime to Avoid Fights instead of running in the Open infront of Stacked Teams\n\n-  ⭕  **Center Zone Timing**\n  * Only claim the dead center if you have the needed Loot and Mats to Help you Survive against The other Teams\n  * Setting up late in the center gets you lobby focused by the spray meta so you should always focus on Rotates in Mid-Game and get into a good spot fast\n\n-  ⭕  **Secure High Ground**\n  * Never box up in low-ground valleys you Should always look for Higher Places to Build or Secure so you wont be Sprayed From other teams\n  *  heavy ARs make low ground a death sentence Which can eliminate you instantly if they kept Spraying you\n  * Base up on mountains or Hills which has a chance of getting you a Refresh if the Mats and Heals are needed\n\n### \uD83C\uDF92 Inventory & Movement\n-     **Prioritize Mobility**\n  * Never edge camp without hard mobility items like Shockwaves most importantly\n  * Make Sure 1 teammate Carries an AR and the Other SMG to Have more Ammo if needed so you wont Run out\n  * Make Sure to Carry Shockwaves in your Loot to stay Away from W-Keying Teams or Rotating to the Next circle",
